Michael Williams (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Williams_(actor) 0 Michael Leonard Williams, KSG (9 July 1935 – 11 January 2001) was an English actor who played both classical and comedy roles. Until his death, he was the husband of actress Dame Judi Dench. Michael_Leonard_Williams , KSG ( 9_July_1935 – 11_January_2001 ) was an_English_actor who played both_classical_and_comedy_roles . Until his_death , he was the_husband of actress_Dame_Judi_Dench .
